data.description: NOT BLOWING SMOKE When We Say That This 4 Bedroom, 2 1/2 Bath, Large 2 Car Garage Semi Contemporary Stucco Home In North McAllen Is A Tremendous Buy. Check The Pictures And Notice The Expansive Living Areas, Large Windows And High Ceilings. This Home Was Built To Make You Smile Every Morning You Wake From Your Dream To Live Your Dream. With An Open Concept Kitchen Overlooking The Living Area, This Is A Home For Interaction, Entertaining And Enjoyable Family Life. The Master Suite Boasts A Lot Of Space And An Additional Sitting Area That Could Also Accommodate A Crib, Desk Or Maybe Even A Treadmill. It Has Everything And More And At A Reasonable Price ;) A Couple Of The Many Cool Things: Backyard Play-Set, Nest Thermostat, Water Softener.....
